"&HVNga;, et need ise liiguksid sisestamiskasti. Kui sul oli õigus, ilmub "
"nähtavale järgmine anagramm, vastasel juhul hüppavad tähed tahvlile tagasi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &kanagram;"
msgstr "&kanagram;i seadistamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Configure</guilabel> dialog is opened by clicking on the "
"<guiicon>Configure</guiicon> button:"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Seadistamis</guilabel>dialoogi saab avada klõpsuga nupule "
"<guiicon>Seadista</guiicon>:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kanagram; general settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kanagram;i üldised seadistused</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kanagram; general settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kanagram;i üldised seadistused</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Auto-hide hints after:</guilabel> drop down box allows you to "
"specify how hints are presented to you. Here, you can set the hint box to "
"disappear after a certain amount of seconds (&eg; 5 seconds), or you can "
"leave it as default (<quote>Do Not Auto-Hide Hints</quote>)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vihjeid näidatakse:</guilabel> <interface>hüpikkast</interface> "
"võimaldab määrata, kuidas sulle vihjeid näidatakse: vihjekasti võib panna "
"kaduma teatud arvu sekundite pärast (&eg; 5 sekundit) või siis jätta kehtima "
"vaikeväärtuse (<quote>Vihjeid ei peideta automaatselt</quote>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guilabel>Time for resolving the anagram:</guilabel> drop down box "
"to specify the time you have to resolve each puzzle. By default there is "
"<quote>No time limit</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Rippmenüüga <guilabel>Anagrammi lahendamise aeg</guilabel> saab määrata iga "
"mõistatuse lahendamiseks ettenähtud aja. Vaikimisi kehtib valik "
"<quote>Ajapiirang puudub</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Play Using:</guilabel> drop down box allows you to play "
"&kanagram; using vocabularies of a different language. For this feature to "
"work, you must have vocabularies of a separate language installed."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Hüpikkast</interface> <guilabel>Kasutatav keel</guilabel> "
"võimaldab &kanagram;is kasutada erinevate keelte sõnastikke. Et seda "
"võimalust pruukida, peab sul olema paigaldatud mitme keele sõnastikke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Set timer for scoring purpose:</guilabel> drop down box "
#| "allows you to set in seconds the time interval of the score timer."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Set timer for scoring purpose:</guilabel> drop down box allows "
"you to set in seconds the time interval of the scoring timer."
msgstr ""
"Rippmenüüs <guilabel>Taimer skoori arvestamiseks</guilabel> saab määrata "
"sekundites skooritaimeri intervalli."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Score Point Settings</guilabel> checkbox can be used to reveal "
"or hide options to configure scoring of answers."
msgstr ""
"Kastikese <guilabel>Skoori arvestamise seadistused</guilabel> märkimisel "
"ilmuvad nähtavale valikud, millega saab täpsustada skoori arvestamise "
"võimalusi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:246
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Use sounds</guilabel> check box allows you to either allow "
#| "or suppress the &kanagram; sound effects."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Use sounds</guilabel> check box allows you to either allow or "
"suppress sound effects."
msgstr ""
"Märkekast <guilabel>Helide kasutamine</guilabel> võimaldab &kanagram;i "
"heliefektid sisse või välja lülitada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Only uppercase letters</guilabel> check box allows you to "
"switch &kanagram; to the uppercase only mode for words on the blackboard."
msgstr ""
"Märkekast <guilabel>Ainult suurtähed</guilabel> võimaldab lülitada &kanagram;"
"i režiimi, kus tahvlil näidatavate sõnade puhul kasutatakse ainult suurtähti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Say correct words</guilabel> check box allows you to turn "
#| "off or on pronunciations. The audio files of the pronunciations should be "
#| "included into the vocabulary being played or you should install and "
#| "configure &jovie; for this option to work."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Say correct words</guilabel> check box allows you to turn "
"pronunciations on or off. The audio files of the pronunciations should be "
"included in the vocabulary being played, or else you should install and "
"configure &jovie; for this option to work."
msgstr ""
"Märkekast <guilabel>Õigete sõnade väljaütlemine</guilabel> võimaldab sõnade "
"kõnelemise sisse või välja lülitada. Hääldamise helifailid peavad olema "
"esitatava sõnastikuga kaasas või siis tuleb paigaldada ja seadistada &jovie;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vocabularies"
msgstr "Sõnastikud"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Vocabularies</guilabel> configuration page allows you to "
"manage your installed vocabularies. Using this dialog, you can <action>edit</"
"action> and <action>remove</action> downloaded vocabularies, as well as "
"<action>create</action> your very own:"
msgstr ""
"Seadistustekaart <guilabel>Sõnastikud</guilabel> võimaldab hallata "
"paigaldatud sõnastikke. Selles dialoogis saab allalaaditud sõnastikke "
"<action>muuta</action> ja <action>eemaldada</action>, samuti <action>luua</"
"action> omaenda sõnastikke:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kanagram; vocabulary settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kanagram;i sõnastikuseadistused</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kanagram; vocabulary settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kanagram;i sõnastikuseadistused</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:285
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guibutton>Create New</guibutton> button <action>opens the <link "
#| "linkend=\"vocab-editor\"><guilabel>Vocabulary Editor</guilabel></link> "
#| "dialog</action> so that you can author your own vocabularies which you "
#| "can then play."
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Create New</guibutton> button <action>opens the <link linkend="
"\"vocab-editor\"><guilabel>Vocabulary Editor</guilabel></link> dialog</"
"action> so that you can author your own vocabularies which you can then play "
"with."
msgstr ""
"Klõps nupule <guibutton>Loo uus</guibutton> <action>avab <link linkend="
"\"vocab-editor\"><guilabel>sõnastikuredaktori</guilabel></link>i</action>, "
"kus saad luua omaenda sõnastiku, mille sõnu seejärel ära arvama asuda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Edit</guibutton> button allows you to <action>make changes to "
"vocabularies that you have either created or downloaded off the Internet</"
"action>."
msgstr ""
"Nupuga <guibutton>Muuda</guibutton> saab <action>muuta sõnastikke, mille "
"oled ise loonud või internetist tõmmanud</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select which vocabulary you would like to apply these actions to by "
"using the <interface>list of vocabularies</interface>."
msgstr ""
"Seda, millise sõnastikuga mainitud toiminguid ette võtta, saab valida "
"<interface>sõnastike nimekirjast</interface>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vocabulary Editor"
msgstr "Sõnastikuredaktor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Vocabulary Editor allows you to create your own vocabularies, which "
"&kanagram; can then test you with:"
msgstr ""
"Sõnastikuredaktor võimaldab luua omaenda sõnastikke, mida &kanagram; "
"seejärel laseb sul läbi mängida:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>&kanagram; <guilabel>Vocabulary Editor</guilabel></screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kanagram;i <guilabel>sõnastikuredaktor</guilabel></screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kanagram; <guilabel>Vocabulary Editor</guilabel></phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kanagram;i <guilabel>sõnastikuredaktor</guilabel></phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Vocabulary Name</guilabel> field lets you <action>name your "
#| "vocabulary</action>."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Vocabulary Name:</guilabel> field lets you <action>name your "
"vocabulary</action>."
msgstr ""
"Väljale <guilabel>Sõnastiku nimi</guilabel> saad <action>kirjutada sõnastiku "
"nime</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:333
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Description</guilabel> field enables you to <action>expand "
#| "on your vocabulary name</action>, providing your user with more details "
#| "of the content of your vocabulary."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Description:</guilabel> field enables you to <action>expand "
"your vocabulary name</action>, providing the user with more details of the "
"content of your vocabulary."
msgstr ""
"Väljal <guilabel>Kirjeldus</guilabel> saad <action>laiendada sõnastiku nime</"
"action>, andes selle kasutajatele rohkem infot sõnastiku sisu kohta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:337
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Try to keep both the name and description fields as short as possible. "
#| "Effective vocabularies cover a narrow, focused set of words for a single "
#| "subject. Try to write at least 20 words for your vocabulary, so that it "
#| "will not be quickly finished by the user."
msgid ""
"Try to keep both the name and description fields as short as possible. "
"Effective vocabularies cover a narrow, focused set of words for a single "
"subject. Try to write at least 20 words for your vocabulary, so that it will "
"not be finished too quickly."
msgstr ""
"Proovi jätta nii nimi kui kirjeldus võimalikult lühikeseks. Head sõnastikud "
"sisaldavad üsna kitsalt konkreetse teemaga määratletud sõnu. Ürita "
"sõnastikku lisada vähemalt 20 sõna, et selle läbimängimine liiga kiiresti ei "
"läheks."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Remove Word</guibutton> button lets you <action>remove words "
"from your vocabulary</action>."
msgstr ""
"Nupp <guibutton>Eemalda sõna</guibutton> võimaldab <action>eemaldada sõna "
"sõnastikust</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>New Word</guibutton> button <action>creates a new word entry "
"in your vocabulary</action>, ready for you to expand."
msgstr ""
"Nupp <guibutton>Uus sõna</guibutton> <action>loob sõnastikku uue kirje ehk "
"sõna</action>, mida saad seejärel täpsustada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:353
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Word</guilabel> field lets you <action>write word values "
#| "into your vocabulary</action>."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Word:</guilabel> field lets you <action>write word values into "
"your vocabulary</action>."
msgstr ""
"Väljale <guilabel>Sõna</guilabel> saad <action>kirjutada sõna enda</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Hint</guilabel> field allows you to <action>write hints to "
"accompany your words</action>."
msgstr ""
"Väljale <guilabel>Vihje</guilabel> saad <action>kirjutada sõnaga kaasneva "
"vihje</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:362
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Good hints clearly, yet subtly describe the word, whilst increasing the "
#| "knowledge of the vocabulary subject for your user. Also ensure that your "
#| "hints are fairly short (under 40 characters in length)."
msgid ""
"Good hints clearly yet subtly describe the word, while also increasing the "
"knowledge of the user. Also ensure that your hints are fairly short (under "
"40 characters in length)."
msgstr ""
"Head vihjed on sellised, mis iseloomustavad sõna ühemõtteliselt, kuid "
"jätavad siiski mõtlemisruumi ja ühtlasi laiendavad teadmisi antud sõna "
"kohta. Ka vihjed peaksid olema suhteliselt lühikesed (mitte pikemad kui 40 "
"tähemärki)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guibutton>Save</guibutton> button <action>saves your vocabulary "
#| "content</action>, and enables its use directly in &kanagram; (it will "
#| "immediately become available within the application, selectable via. the "
#| "<interface>Vocabulary Selector</interface>)."
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Save</guibutton> button <action>saves your new vocabulary "
"content</action>, and enables its use directly in &kanagram; (it will "
"immediately become available within the application, selectable via. the "
"<interface>Vocabulary Selector</interface>)."
msgstr ""
"Nupp <guibutton>Salvesta</guibutton> <action>salvestab sõnastiku</action> ja "
"võimaldab &kanagram;il seda kohe kasutama hakata (seda saab kohe hakata "
"kasutama <interface>sõnastiku valija</interface> abil)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:373
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guibutton>Close</guibutton> button <action>closes the "
#| "<guilabel>Vocabulary Editor</guilabel> dialog</action> without saving the "
#| "content of your vocabulary."
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Close</guibutton> button <action>closes the "
"<guilabel>Vocabulary Editor</guilabel> dialog</action> without saving the "
"content of your new or modified vocabulary."
msgstr ""
"Nupp <guibutton>Sulge</guibutton> <action>sulgeb "
"<guilabel>sõnastikuredaktori</guilabel></action> ilma sõnastiku sisu "
"salvestamata."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Stuff"
msgstr "Uus kraam"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Download new vocabulary</guibutton> button on the "
"<guilabel>Vocabularies</guilabel> configuration page allows you to obtain "
"new vocabulary files from the Internet:"
msgstr ""
"Nupp <guibutton>Laadi alla uus sõnaraamat</guibutton> kaardil "
"<guilabel>Sõnaraamatud</guilabel> võimaldab uusi sõnastikefaile internetist "
"hankida:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kanagram; new stuff dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kanagram;i uue kraami dialoog</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kanagram; new stuff dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kanagram;i uue kraami dialoog</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To install a vocabulary from the Internet, click on the vocabulary item in "
"the list, then press the <guibutton>Install</guibutton> button to install to "
"your system. The downloaded vocabulary will then be available to play "
"immediately."
msgstr ""
"Sõnastiku paigaldamiseks internetist klõpsa nimekirjas huvipakkuval "
"sõnastikul ja vajuta seejärel nuppu <guibutton>Paigalda</guibutton>. "
"Tõmmatud ja paigaldatud sõnastikku saab otsekohe kasutama hakata."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have already downloaded a vocabulary this button will change to "
"<guibutton>Uninstall</guibutton> which allows you to remove a vocabulary."
msgstr ""
"Kui oled juba mõne sõnastiku alla laadinud, võtab see nupp kuju "
"<guibutton>Eemalda</guibutton>, millega saab sõnastiku eemaldada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:407
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To get more information about a vocabulary like the author, a description "
#| "about the content and the changelog press the <guibutton>Details</"
#| "guibutton> button."
msgid ""
"To get more information about a vocabulary like the author, a description "
"about the content, and the changelog, press the <guibutton>Details</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Täpsemat teavet sõnastiku kohta, näiteks autori, sisu kirjelduse ja "
"muudatuste logi, annab klõps nupule <guibutton>Üksikasjad</guibutton>."

